{"tid":2350890,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港年青人，我地無時間再傷春悲秋","createTime":"2021-01-02T17:06:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T13:48:20.000Z","uid":278783,"like":26,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9d84e82c26478621e50deb11c48c60f619224dee","tid":2350890,"uid":278783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T17:06:39.000Z","msg":"香港年青人我地真係無時間再傷春悲秋 <br />\n<br />\n太過學術性既分析我唔曉 但從種種跡象香港地位既衰落已經成為必然 <br />\n<br />\n無論大陸用其他城市取代香港地位或者世界圍堵大陸也好 香港亦一併會受到波及<br />\n<br />\n但以上兩種局面由施行到正式實行 應該仲有幾年時間<br />\n<br />\n年青人您地要認清以下幾點：<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\">1.自回歸以後 香港已經係只適合搵錢既地方 而唔係安居既地方<br />\n<br />\n2.世界既本質係弱肉強食 <br />\n<br />\n3.唔好再幻想邊個會打救香港 從來只有自救先係上策<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n依家可以做既野只有：<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"gold\">1.好好裝備自己 放闊眼光 <br />\n<br />\n2.我地Proud of自己價值觀同時首先要確保自己有能力唔好比人輕易擊倒<br />\n<br />\n3.讀書既努力讀書 趁住香港呢個名仲有價值既時候 為移民鋪路<br />\n職場上既積極做事 視所有您認為討厭既藍絲為競爭對手 將佢地視為踏腳石 </span></span> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上所有種種都係為左往外鋪路 <br />\n<span class=\"maroon\"><span class=\"x-large\">既然香港已經比中上層個班人玩殘左 咁就等我地渣乾香港最後既價值 然後走資離開香港</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n最後強調多次<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\">香港係只適合搵錢既地方 而唔係安居既地方 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">同埋唔撚好再講我好撚鍾意香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />DLLM <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"pink\">我地愛既只係同一價值觀既香港人</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">願與同一價值觀香港人共榮焉 他日異地再聚</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"maroon\">另祝藍絲廢老們永與大灣區共存亡</span>"},{"pid":"56b9fd6212737fe8dd5d842a4aa0833925314309","tid":2350890,"uid":38172,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T17:08:31.000Z","msg":"講就易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"900de82d2529ff553b863d3caf8b4edaef3f344f","tid":2350890,"uid":278783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T17:12:16.000Z","msg":"放長雙眼睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有人睇好自然有人唔睇好"},{"pid":"66f38e93b0a592de8a8de34035b3b8b007d1d0c8","tid":2350890,"uid":278783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T17:12:44.000Z","msg":"歡迎理性討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2c0676eee5279021cd4188b267e3cfb25d8b3f","tid":2350890,"uid":38172,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"66f38e93b0a592de8a8de34035b3b8b007d1d0c8","tid":2350890,"uid":278783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T17:12:44.000Z","msg":"歡迎理性討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T17:14:04.000Z","msg":"有咩好理性討論je,  你都set左前設 其他人講咩都無用架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63feab928c283c4b4b411e8aa3f551c2d3c47d1","tid":2350890,"uid":269202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T17:14:17.000Z","msg":"我覺得星期六日去做工作或興趣工作係基本，草多個錢去台灣"},{"pid":"89c15be5db1ed12a07f729a54875e8977998a5c6","tid":2350890,"uid":278783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c2c0676eee5279021cd4188b267e3cfb25d8b3f","tid":2350890,"uid":38172,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"66f38e93b0a592de8a8de34035b3b8b007d1d0c8","tid":2350890,"uid":278783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T17:12:44.000Z","msg":"歡迎理性討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T17:14:04.000Z","msg":"有咩好理性討論je,  你都set左前設 其他人講咩都無用架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T17:16:47.000Z","msg":"推下文禮貌性咁講姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e90b01517d4cfcbc6c1fbbcb2f11eabdf8ecadc","tid":2350890,"uid":278783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f63feab928c283c4b4b411e8aa3f551c2d3c47d1","tid":2350890,"uid":2692